  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>Released 04/10/2018 CT 2:15pm CT (19:15 UTC)</p><p>We added a few new options to the ticket receipt print settings:</p><h2 id=\"id-1.13.13-NewTicketReceiptOptions\">New Ticket Receipt Options</h2><ul><li><p>Added &quot;Hide totals&quot; toggle option, which when checked should hide the totals section</p></li></ul><h2 id=\"id-1.13.13-NewTicketEmailedReceiptOptions\">New Ticket Emailed Receipt Options</h2><ul><li><p>Added &quot;Ticket Number&quot;, &quot;Ticket Barcode&quot;, and &quot;Ticket URL&quot; as toggles</p></li><li><p>Added &quot;Hide totals&quot; toggle option, which when checked should hide the totals section</p></li></ul>",
